title: Making Sense of the Texans' Wild Weekend | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
Kevin Clark and Robert Mays examine Houston's recent all-in moves, including their franchise-altering trade for Laremy Tunsil and decision to trade Jadeveon Clowney for pennies on the dollar. The guys then analyze what the moves mean for the Seahawks' short-term hopes and the Dolphins' long-term plans before sorting out some other odds and ends from cutdown day.
